Title: Boots on the Ground
Description:
Just who I wanted to see.

I have a requisition script for items of leather from some of the denizens of the Dream. Shoes, of course. Bipeds tend to go through them like a bird through the forest, yes?

Once you have acquired them, please take them to Cylania.
ObjectivesText: Deliver 3 Pioneer's Leather Boots to Cylania in the Emerald Dream.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver 3 Pioneer's Leather Boots to Cylania in the Emerald Dream

Objectives.Text: Complete the events of "Enter the Dream"
